Medyo deep, but, I was so inspired by Direk Paul Soriano video @paulsoriano1017 and I want to share this with you guys, kaya panoorin nyo and be inspired.

#CAMON17 #CTheBestOfYou #TECNOMobile @tecnomobileph

node.text:
Eighteen 💟

Thank you so much to everyone who greeted me!! Still thankful that even though this isn’t how i planned my 18th birthday to be everything still happened way better than I expected even with this quarantine going on. To my fans, thank you for always being there for me 💜 I started in this industry as an extra when i was young with no fan base at all. And now i have 11M to thank. Maraming maraming salamat po ✨

✍️ by @charised_ ✨

I only want the best for my babies, Oreo, Chewy and Marley! 🐶 That’s why I always make sure to give them the right food with complete & balanced nutrition. And today, I prepared a special POWER MIX Meal for my dogs with the combination of their favorite Pedigree Mini and Pedigree Pouch! And it looks so yummy! ☺️

Guys! Do you want  to try Pedigree Mini 400 grams and Pedigree Pouch for FREE? The first 100 who will comment their most creative answer on “why should your dog try the mixing recipe?” Will receive the sampling product and be delivered to your home! Promo will run until 30 days only. So Comment na kayo! 🤩

If you want to buy it, Pedigree products are now available on Lazada, Shopee and Pandamart. Goodluck and always stay safe! 😉

node.text:
Hi everyone!! in celebration of world Aspin day i would like everyone to meet Kookie 💟 I witnessed her transformation first hand and it was one of the best things I’ve seen!!! She never failed to let us know how grateful she is and we’re just so happy to have her. I hope this post inspires everyone to adopt their own aspin or puspin. 

Kookie has gained over 3times her previous weight and is getting showered with love everyday now. She’s also getting along with our other aspins Cheese and Sasha 💖
🥺🥰😭
Happy National Aspin Day 
#adoptdontshop #cleantheshelters #aspinclub #aspinday #nationalaspinday
